Deputy Director Mao has already
obtained permission

00:39:26.960 --> 00:39:27.730
from Chairman Chiang

00:39:28.400 --> 00:39:30.440
and ordered me to search
all Gu family's properties,

00:39:30.700 --> 00:39:31.750
including the Gu Residence.

00:39:36.840 --> 00:39:39.980
You're saying our family
harbors traitors.

00:39:42.080 --> 00:39:45.250
You even got Chairman Chiang's
permission

00:39:45.270 --> 00:39:46.460
to search our home.

00:39:49.560 --> 00:39:50.250
Permission, huh?

00:39:51.500 --> 00:39:52.540
Where's the search warrant?

00:39:58.530 --> 00:39:58.860
Luo Han,

00:39:58.880 --> 00:40:02.340
I know you're the Deputy Chief now.

00:40:03.440 --> 00:40:05.340
It's normal for you
to have official duties.

00:40:06.000 --> 00:40:07.440
I can allow you to search our home,

00:40:07.880 --> 00:40:09.500
but only you go in alone.

00:40:09.520 --> 00:40:11.980
If they all want to go in,

00:40:12.300 --> 00:40:14.200
then you'd better think
about the consequences.

00:40:16.300 --> 00:40:17.650
I decide what the consequences are.

00:40:18.560 --> 00:40:19.170
Fine.

00:40:21.000 --> 00:40:21.250
Go.

00:40:22.000 --> 00:40:22.350
Yes, sir.

00:40:27.080 --> 00:40:28.090
How dare you, Gu Yangshan!

00:40:32.000 --> 00:40:34.090
Sorry, my aim was off.

00:40:34.520 --> 00:40:35.340
I should kill you.

00:40:37.670 --> 00:40:39.500
Come on, who else wants to try?

00:40:42.600 --> 00:40:43.840
The moment you fired this shot,

00:40:44.080 --> 00:40:45.860
